# Streamlit Secrets Template
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .streamlit/secrets.toml
# Do NOT commit the real secrets.toml to GitHub
# Add secrets via Streamlit Cloud → App Settings → Secrets
